{"tid":671400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抹窗失重心　女子墮樓亡","createTime":"2018-05-20T06:15:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T02:13:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"506be4cf5bd7ccde6c9665e8152660afae50b4c8","tid":671400,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:15:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180520/20396214\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180520%2F20396214&d=nDvskFM%2FCnaCO%2FvNG493ckkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=082023b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180520%2F20396214&h=3a299966\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180520/20396214</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月20日 <br />\n<br />\n抹窗失重心　女子墮樓亡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180520/large/20la5p99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180520%2Flarge%2F20la5p99.jpg&h=db87e2d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■大圍愉景花園有女子墮斃，警員到場調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名中年女子昨晚在大圍一屋苑單位抹窗時，疑俯身太出失重心墮樓，倒卧大廈對開。其丈夫揭發事件但為時已晚，連忙報警，惜警員到場證實女事主當場死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n夫在屋內未為意<br />\n<br />\n墮樓身亡女子姓鄧(50歲)，與家人同住大圍翠田街1至3號愉景花園C座一單位。昨晚7時許，鄧婦在家中抹窗，疑不慎失重心，結果整個人跌出窗外墮樓。現場消息稱，事發時鄧婦的59歲姓周丈夫也在屋內，但未為意妻子墮樓，稍後發現妻子不在屋內，望出窗外赫見她倒臥樓下平台後報警。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，惟證實鄧婦頭爆肢折，當地死亡。警方調查後相信鄧婦抹窗期間意外墮下，事件無可疑。事後仵工把遺體移送殮房。<br />\n<br />\n專家提醒抹窗要注意5點：安裝穩固窗花，抹窗時關上窗花；勿打開、依着窗花或玻璃工作；如無窗花，必須腳踏實地抹窗，不應站凳上；伸手不伸人，不可將身體伸出窗外；需要時用長柄工具，加設手帶防飛脫等。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黎家駒  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n迷幻男危站　失足倒吊簷篷<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n青年攜電動板車跳橋死"},{"pid":"7b8ba0752ac118e7b2f77db0a389e3b6c1cf5cff","tid":671400,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:18:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd317be7aa200e976b31644ab59d55d41373db47","tid":671400,"uid":67500,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T12:52:26.000Z","msg":"年年都有人咁死，中年女人唔撚睇時事新聞，妹下妹下，成撚日抹抹抹，抹你老母咩"},{"pid":"29899d6d694acefdb14a3ea8d719ffa9823020a2","tid":671400,"uid":60787,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T12:54:36.000Z","msg":"啲女人唔夠手長走去抹窗真係好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58b3d22c9800f673eb614f48f8ea2cd60b77a17b","tid":671400,"uid":20227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T12:55:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"389b8737b0f2c971d0dce5d21b48e3b7208313e7","tid":671400,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T12:55:56.000Z","msg":"抹嚟做乜呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a61c81cab089918354a39144d5c6c8ef3d1f3325","tid":671400,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"389b8737b0f2c971d0dce5d21b48e3b7208313e7","tid":671400,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T12:55:56.000Z","msg":"抹嚟做乜呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T13:03:43.000Z","msg":"負資產冇錢<br />\n日日係屋企得閒抹下窗好正常姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa028b14b3c259f14b2d540e21feb3680cd09831","tid":671400,"uid":8957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T13:06:39.000Z","msg":"咁多人可以抹窗跌落街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"949641e4c85689080ecc436c1eb5cd744274bf30","tid":671400,"uid":20072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T13:07:08.000Z","msg":"抹窗真係好ON9"},{"pid":"4c6d2c605f7caed288a2f250950ccbd6c0d32100","tid":671400,"uid":12267,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T13:09:00.000Z",